LMNTShCh 'yLMVTh LBN MZMVUr LDVD.
'aVDH YHVH BKL-LBY 'aSPhUrH KL-NPhL'aVThYK.
'aShMChH V'a'yLTShH BK 'aZMUrH ShMK 'yLYVN.
BShVB-'aVYBY 'aChVUr YKShLV VY'aBDV MPhNYK.
KY-'yShYTh MShPhTY VDYNY YShBTh LKS'a ShVPhT TShDQ.
G'yUrTh GVYM 'aBDTh UrSh'y ShMM MChYTh L'yVLM V'yD.
H'aVYB ThMV ChUrBVTh LNTShCh V'yUrYM NThShTh 'aBD ZKUrM HMH.
VYHVH L'yVLM YShB KVNN LMShPhT KS'aV.
VHV'a YShPhT-ThBL BTShDQ YDYN L'aMYM BMYShUrYM.
VYHY YHVH MShGB LDK MShGB L'yThVTh BTShUrH.
VYBTChV BK YVD'yY ShMK KY L'a-'yZBTh DUrShYK YHVH.
ZMUrV LYHVH YShB TShYVN HGYDV B'yMYM 'yLYLVThYV.
KY-DUrSh DMYM 'aVThM ZKUr L'a-ShKCh TSh'yQTh 'yNYYM.
ChNNNY YHVH Ur'aH 'yNYY MShN'aY MUrVMMY MSh'yUrY MVTh.
LM'yN 'aSPhUrH KL-ThHLThYK BSh'yUrY BTh-TShYVN 'aGYLH BYShV'yThK.
TB'yV GVYM BShChTh 'yShV BUrShTh-ZV TMNV NLKDH UrGLM.
NVD'y YHVH MShPhT 'yShH BPh'yL KPhYV NVQSh UrSh'y HGYVN SLH.
YShVBV UrSh'yYM LSh'aVLH KL-GVYM ShKChY 'aLHYM.
KY L'a LNTShCh YShKCh 'aBYVN ThQVTh 'yNVYM Th'aBD L'yD.
